AUSO.BA.summary: Autopistas Del Sol SA engages in the construction, expansion, remodeling, preservation, maintenance, operation, and administration of highways. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in San Isidro, Argentina.

OEST.BA.summary: Grupo Concesionario del Oeste S.A. engages in the construction, improvement, repair, conservation, extension, remodeling, maintenance, administration, and exploitation of the Western highway in Argentina. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Buenos Aires, Argentina.
